  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the efficacy of KIDNET versus a Meditation/Relaxation
      protocol in treating traumatized children in Sri Lanka when applied by locally trained
      teacher counsellors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
